<td style="width:77%; text-align:center;"><h1 style="font-size:23px; text-align:center;">Hike in Bar practising fees stirs up controversy amongst legal professionals</h1>
<h2 style="font-weight:normal;font-size:12px;"><span class="span_detail">Posted:</span>
3 years ago</h2>
</td>
</tr>
